title: Camp WeWow Music Week Day 4
description:
It's Music Week at Camp WeWow! Warm up those vocals Campers, because today, we're praciting our animal sounds! Visit tinkercast.com/resource/game-the-who-made-that-sound-game for directions to today's activity and share your animal impressions at tinkercast.com/share! Do you know a non-musical item that you think should be a musical instrument?! Tells us all about it at 1-888-7WOW-WOW! You just might get featured around the Camp WeWow Campfire tomorrow!

See Privacy Policy at https://art19.com/privacy and California Privacy Notice at https://art19.com/privacy#do-not-sell-my-info.
